                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Please give a complete date output for reproduction from the created and the changed date.\r\nComplete outputs can be created by $date->getIso() as described in the manual and the FAQ.\r\n\r\nThe patch is not accepted as it breaks existing tests.",
